    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir海外ツアー追加公演の少し前",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……ふふ……！\nもー、頑張り過ぎだよ……えぇー！",
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　愛の声だ……誰かと話してるのか？\n随分楽しそうだが……愛しかいないな",
      "startTime": 14.3392074555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは食べちゃダメなやつなのでは……！\n……えっ、美味しい！？　えぇ～～！！",
      "startTime": 21.7811554335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "通話中、なのか……？　人の出入りもあるし\n少し声量を落としてもらった方がいいかもな",
      "startTime": 29.6562005691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "そっ、そんな所に身一つで飛び込むなんて……！\nあ、危なーーい！",
      "startTime": 36.4079265856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "愛、少し声を落として……聞こえてないのか？\n愛。……あーいー！　……愛ーー！！",
      "startTime": 43.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあっ！？　びっくりした！\nえっ、え、{user}さん！？",
      "startTime": 49.3960097631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "すすす、すみません！\nイヤホンをしていたので気付きませんでした！",
      "startTime": 52.9960097631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、こっちも大声をあげてすまない\n一体何をしてたんだ？",
      "startTime": 58.6999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}